title: Echo Movement Complete Disccography
description:
After years of searching, multiple false download links, and giving my credit card info to more than one sketchy website, I bring you every Echo Movement album!

Contains:
Echo Movement(S/T)
On My Way
In The Ocean
Music Played On
Love And The Human Outreach

Finding all of these was quite difficult so I'm posting this here to save all my fellow Echo Movement fans the pain I went through to acquire them all. Enjoy!
